technology we call QuickType.

1090
00:56:52,189 --> 00:56:53,056
Oh.

1091
00:56:53,056 --> 00:56:54,825
[ Laughter ]

1092
00:56:54,825 --> 00:56:59,162
So, prior to iPhone, this
was the state-of-the-art

1093
00:56:59,162 --> 00:57:00,631
