QuickType supports predictive

1101
00:57:28,158 --> 00:57:29,693
typing suggestions.

1102
00:57:29,693 --> 00:57:32,596
So, as you type,
you get suggestions

1103
00:57:32,596 --> 00:57:34,631
for the next words you
might want to type,

1104
00:57:34,631 --> 00:57:38,168
and you can tap things out
faster than ever before

1105
00:57:38,168 --> 00:57:40,337
and it's incredibly smart.

1106
00:57:40,337 --> 00:57:42,406
So, it's context sensitive.

1107
00:57:42,406 --> 00:57:44,308
For instance in messages,
if someone asks you,

1108
00:57:44,308 --> 00:57:45,609
