01:39:34,715 --> 01:39:37,518
Tim, come on up.

1904
01:39:37,518 --> 01:39:44,692
[ Applause ]

1905
01:39:44,692 --> 01:39:46,260
Thank you.

1906
01:39:46,260 --> 01:39:48,463
We've had the opportunity
to work with Metal

1907
01:39:48,463 --> 01:39:50,298
and to illustrate some
of the possibilities,

