01:41:34,168 --> 01:41:36,604
but of course not
going to stop there.

1949
01:41:36,604 --> 01:41:38,606
So I can touch the screen
to call more of them to me

1950
01:41:38,606 --> 01:41:39,740
and then guide them
around the area.

1951
01:41:39,740 --> 01:41:43,744
So there are about 3,500
individually animated

1952
01:41:43,744 --> 01:41:45,146
and rendered butterfly
